{"tid":482882,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"天蠍入，不限絲或巴！","createTime":"2017-11-28T14:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T05:23:18.000Z","uid":159604,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9265bbe9d4c4a49ce72fb0b22bfbbd9f062407b8","tid":482882,"uid":159604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T14:37:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時候會特然自悲<br />\n明明傾得幾好<br />\n但自悲嗰個感覺一嚟<br />\n就心諗唔好害人啦<br />\n然後就唔復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但其實我都好中意你"},{"pid":"47ac155910364810ed211be25e403d8146222c5a","tid":482882,"uid":76972,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T14:55:40.000Z","msg":"突然<br />\n唔覆<br />\n鍾意"},{"pid":"58f214db2be6d4487d59c73605f301cda2c697c9","tid":482882,"uid":76972,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T14:55:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>突然<br />\n唔覆<br />\n鍾意</blockquote><br />\n自卑"},{"pid":"18df0ff17502ff2fbc6d67f33725a396204119d3","tid":482882,"uid":159604,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T15:04:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>突然<br />\n唔覆<br />\n鍾意</blockquote><br />\n自卑</blockquote><br />\n正字刑警咩<br />\n睇得明就得啦"},{"pid":"7d937b41ac0e657a170b21b014ce574df6db506f","tid":482882,"uid":131031,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T15:12:41.000Z","msg":"賴乜野星座阿<br />\n明明自己又唔差<br />\n夾硬搵位入自己<br />\n屌，真係好撚on9<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(雖然我都係咁)"},{"pid":"38a895ad4b1b813484b6b2f063db21f3361eb569","tid":482882,"uid":159604,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T05:12:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賴乜野星座阿<br />\n明明自己又唔差<br />\n夾硬搵位入自己<br />\n屌，真係好撚on9<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(雖然我都係咁)</blockquote><br />\n其實好心up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明都中意對方"},{"pid":"023ca3344194adc6de081a371b717b0a8061fc84","tid":482882,"uid":67802,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T05:53:28.000Z","msg":"成日都唔知自己諗乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似上個星期同女朋友分手咁<br />\n明明佢第二日黎搵我cool煲<br />\n佢喊到仆街咁 我都無動於衷<br />\n但今日又會想搵番佢<br />\n都唔知係因為對佢仲有感情 掛住佢定只係自己內疚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得天蠍咁黑人憎係因為我地成日都唔知自己點諗<br />\n跟住係未搞清楚自己諗咩既情況下就做左個決定出黎<br />\n點知個決定跟本就唔係心入面既諗法 <br />\n到最後就傷害到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以我地都係安份守己做番個毒撚算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828b9c7afd9df2b2104780e4a2da9330aa48551d","tid":482882,"uid":49092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:17:31.000Z","msg":"More"},{"pid":"17e381219f3c6f8b8f86575140598eb0f019be6b","tid":482882,"uid":129829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:20:19.000Z","msg":"天蠍=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594dd4f6ba299f4db36a2adaafa629357858e8c0","tid":482882,"uid":28567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:22:26.000Z","msg":"天蠍留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26468e4b4b864b8a377768a477c0e1361848e494","tid":482882,"uid":91326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:44:18.000Z","msg":"記仇"},{"pid":"30bc707a150324068cb897c68265c3730e6d577b","tid":482882,"uid":89660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:50:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>突然<br />\n唔覆<br />\n鍾意</blockquote><br />\n自卑</blockquote><br />\n正字刑警咩<br />\n睇得明就得啦</blockquote><br />\n字都唔識多隻唔怪得咁自卑啦呀天蠍暖男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a8cd448bf805366a463311a448c6ceeabf9d05","tid":482882,"uid":159604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T09:33:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日都唔知自己諗乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似上個星期同女朋友分手咁<br />\n明明佢第二日黎搵我cool煲<br />\n佢喊到仆街咁 我都無動於衷<br />\n但今日又會想搵番佢<br />\n都唔知係因為對佢仲有感情 掛住佢定只係自己內疚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得天蠍咁黑人憎係因為我地成日都唔知自己點諗<br />\n跟住係未搞清楚自己諗咩既情況下就做左個決定出黎<br />\n點知個決定跟本就唔係心入面既諗法 <br />\n到最後就傷害到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以我地都係安份守己做番個毒撚算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明呀爸打<br />\n有時其實都好中意對方<br />\n但又因為面子或自卑<br />\n做咗一啲令自己後悔嘅決定"},{"pid":"9c94a14bba141878ed5bbd9930d3631cfd78bdc1","tid":482882,"uid":159604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T09:36:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記仇</blockquote><br />\n呢個真！雖然唔會係塊面度表現出嚟，但我心入已經講緊粗口，一直記得！<br />\n<br />\n仲有一有機會我就一定報仇，但人地如果好誠懇咁道歉，我又會心軟原諒佢"},{"pid":"e4306d3a7286e3eb9443b044dbc54ce5faf71fc5","tid":482882,"uid":159604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T09:36:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>突然<br />\n唔覆<br />\n鍾意</blockquote><br />\n自卑</blockquote><br />\n正字刑警咩<br />\n睇得明就得啦</blockquote><br />\n字都唔識多隻唔怪得咁自卑啦呀天蠍暖男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你咪繼續"},{"pid":"14e6cea3445f33fa1654f7e7333f74435ce8a43d","tid":482882,"uid":160523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T09:41:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>記仇</blockquote><br />\n呢個真！雖然唔會係塊面度表現出嚟，但我心入已經講緊粗口，一直記得！<br />\n<br />\n仲有一有機會我就一定報仇，但人地如果好誠懇咁道歉，我又會心軟原諒佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀，成日衰心軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9992d